---
@META
dir: skillsPraut/src/templates
updated: 2026-04-15
files: 10
stack: React, Remotion, TypeScript, @remotion/transitions

@EXPORTS
CaseStudyTemplate.tsx: CaseStudyTemplate(episodeNumber, hook, problem, solution, implementation, results)
ComparisonTemplate.tsx: ComparisonTemplate(episodeNumber, hook, leftName, rightName, leftSummary, rightSummary, sideBySide, recommendation)
DeepDiveTemplate.tsx: DeepDiveTemplate(episodeNumber, hook, chapters: {number,title,body}[])
ExplainerTemplate.tsx: ExplainerTemplate(episodeNumber, episodeTitle?, hook, term, definition, example, takeaway, nextVideoTitle?)
MythBustingTemplate.tsx: MythBustingTemplate(episodeNumber, hook, myth, reality, evidence, conclusion)
NewsTemplate.tsx: NewsTemplate(episodeNumber, headline, context, details, impact, opinion)
ReviewTemplate.tsx: ReviewTemplate(episodeNumber, productName, hook, pros[], cons[], demo, verdict)
ShortTemplate.tsx: ShortTemplate(hook, punchline, cta?)
TopTenTemplate.tsx: TopTenTemplate(episodeNumber, hook, items: {title, description?}[])
TutorialTemplate.tsx: TutorialTemplate(episodeNumber, episodeTitle, hook, steps: {title, description?, icon?}[], nextVideoTitle?)

@PROCESSES
video-flow: Hook (HookCard 90f) → TransitionSeries fade × content slides → EndScreen (120f)
short-flow: Hook → Punchline → optional CTA via slide transition (60s total)
tutorial-flow: Hook → Heading → Steps × 60f each → Outro

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: components/frame/{PrautVideoFrame, PrautShortFrame, ExplainerSlide, SlideRoot} | components/chapters/{HookCard, ChapterCard, EndScreen} | components/cards/{ComparisonCard} | components/lists/{MythVsFact, ProsConsTable, StepByStep, TopTenReveal} | components/typography/{DisplayHeading, BodyText, KeyTakeaway} | components/educational/{DefinitionBox} | components/cta/{SubscribeButton} | styles/tokens
external: @remotion/transitions (TransitionSeries, linearTiming, fade, slide)

@STANDARDS
- All templates wrap in PrautVideoFrame (ShortTemplate → PrautShortFrame)
- Fade transitions with timing.medium (24f) — ShortTemplate uses slide
- Hook phase = 90 frames (3s) | ChapterCard = 60 frames (2s) | EndScreen = 120 frames (4s)
- Templates are composable building blocks — pair with compositions in Root.tsx
- Typical structure: Hook → body sections → Outro
---
